2725 Sand Hill RdMenlo Park, CA 94025


        (650) 234-5592
    






We had our account here for a number of years. In my view, Morgan Stanley was not responsive when the pipeline sector began to decline in 2015. When we were critical, our concerns were addressed by a risk manager and our requests for copies or correspondence were declined.  A subsequent demand for damages was declined by Morgan Stanley lawyers.  The amounts are not insignificant, but the cost of lawyering up to go head-to-head against this huge firm and its lawyers is not something we will incur.  So, this is the end of the dispute.







            Morgan Stanley
        






