 Menlo Park - Morgan Stanley -  Menlo Park, CAMorgan Stanley Menlo Park 2775 Sand Hill Road Suite 120 Menlo Park, CA 94025Branch(650) 926-7600Fax(650) 926-7680Toll-free(800) 624-7248Contact UsRequest an AppointmentRequest InformationLogin to Your AccountsOur Branch LocationsWelcomeFind a Financial ProfessionalManaging WealthClients First ApproachWhat Clients Can ExpectOur Financial AdvisorsIn Our CommunitySports Wealth Advisory ServicesNewsletters & BrochuresCareers at Morgan StanleyJoin the TeamA Focused ApproachDedicated Management TeamA Premier PlatformSpecialist Guided Transition ServicesAdvanced Business Building ToolsRobust Marketing ResourcesFar Reaching Global ResourcesComprehensive Professional DevelopmentFinancial Advisor Associate ProgramIn Our CommunityDiversityComprehensive CapabilitiesMap & DirectionsReserved Living & GivingPrivate BankerMarket Information Delayed 20 MinutesWelcome to the Morgan Stanley  Menlo Park Branch
For more than 30 years, Morgan Stanley*’s Menlo Park office has served a wide range of distinguished clients from major corporations, private equity and venture capital firms to senior corporate executives, sophisticated investors, and high net worth families. These clients have relied on our experience and resources to help them meet their financial needs and objectives.Financial Advisors in the Menlo Park office often meld their skills to work on teams that are led by an Advisor with usually more than 20 years of tenure with the firm. Each Financial Advisor is committed to providing our clients with personalized service and astute counsel. Our Financial Advisors are also supported by the extensive resources of Morgan Stanley*, one of the world’s largest, most respected financial services firms. Since joining Morgan Stanley Smith Barney in 1995, I have had the opportunity to witness various economic cycles and investment climates. I am confident that our Financial Advisors possess the discipline and wisdom to help you meet the challenges of our changing environment and take full advantage of the opportunities it presents. I look forward to meeting you and inviting you to consult with our Financial Advisors in the near future.Scott D. RashManaging Director, Wealth ManagementComplex ManagerFamily Wealth DirectorCERTIFIED FINANCIAL PLANNER


