        6/2/2009
    








First to Review
        


I would suggest using anybody but these guys, there customer service is beyond poor, and they could not have been more incompetent, inept if they tried.  I am not a difficult person, but the way these guys treat people is beyond poor.  I had an account with them for over 8 years, in that time several of the advisors I worked with left, it would take them approx 6 months to notify me each time.  There advise at times was good, but the when things went bad they freaked out and acted like it was my fault.  I have never been treated so poorly from an institution as with this one.  I would strongly encourage anyone interested in using this office to consider another one, as well as double check the credentials of your chosen advisor.  They even shipped my account to a call center in Utah when I finally decided to close my account.  They did not even have the courtesy to take care of the issue themselves even though the call center in Utah said they could have.




