                        Investment Management
                    
                
Morgan Stanley strives to provide outstanding long-term investment performance, service, and a comprehensive suite of investment management solutions to a diverse client base, which includes governments, institutions, corporations and individuals worldwide.







Private Credit & Equity
Direct and multi-manager private debt and equity investing focusing on middle market companies,
secondaries and co-investments




Solutions & Multi-Asset
Custom portfolios and alpha-oriented investment strategies tailored to the needs of institutional and
high net worth investors




Real Assets
Decades of investment experience in global real estate and infrastructure with strategies spanning
public and private markets




Global Liquidity
Global cash management solutions for institutional clients




Global Fixed Income
Actively managed single sector and multi-sector strategies across the global fixed income markets





Active Fundamental Equity
Differentiated, high-conviction portfolios that seek to generate attractive returns across global equity
markets









